{"tid":754203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2018年07月24日  今日焦點●即聽","createTime":"2018-07-24T08:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T08:26:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"18ced66200a6af3173e348ff935f2a386eb5f184","tid":754203,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T08:26:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180724/20458917\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180724%2F20458917&d=dvfv8g2v7mlOHxVCz%2Bi7ujCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=b6f70c3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180724%2F20458917&h=49951e97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180724/20458917</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月24日 <br />\n今日焦點●即聽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要聞<br />\n‧長生年使六億行賄<br />\n‧區議會劃界大陰謀<br />\n‧海陸空搜救滑翔男<br />\n‧警破倫敦金拘54人<br />\n<br />\n兩岸國際<br />\n‧習像潑墨女被精神病<br />\n‧多倫多槍擊15死傷<br />\n‧東京都錄得逾40℃<br />\n<br />\n評論<br />\n‧李平〈蘋論〉<br />\n‧李怡〈世道人生〉<br />\n‧鍾劍華論民族黨<br />\n‧盧峯論中美貿易戰<br />\n<br />\n財經<br />\n‧發鈔行新鈔今日公佈<br />\n‧新股遇冷鐵塔恐淡靜<br />\n‧蔡少芬囍匯2.2萬租出<br />\n‧人幣轉跌離岸價穿6.8<br />\n<br />\n體育<br />\n‧亞運港隊獎金加碼<br />\n‧奧斯爾退出德國隊<br />\n‧車仔新帥日食80支煙<br />\n<br />\n娛樂<br />\n‧張錦程用聲冧掂老婆<br />\n‧陳志雲踩港姐質素<br />\n‧柯有倫拍片求婚成功<br />\n<br />\n果籽<br />\n‧價值7百萬的SUV<br />\n‧港媽自製playbook<br />\n‧英文好唔係靠做補充  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片： 誤兇地頭蟲　紅Van佬遭拆水撥"}]}